    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "Hey everyone! \ud83d\udc4b You\u2019ve seriously got to check out this absolute gem. I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it\u2019s honestly in pristine, showroom-level shape\u2014inside and out! It drives like a total dream and looks even better in person. I'm looking for a smooth, easy sale, so I'm offering this beauty at a really competitive price for such a flawless ride. First person to see it will definitely fall in love! Let's get you behind the wheel! \ud83d\ude97\u2728",
