    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_19_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_19",
      "description": "Presenting a museum-grade 1997 Mazda RX-7 FD3S, a pinnacle of 90s JDM engineering. This specimen features the legendary 13B-REW sequential twin-turbocharged rotary engine, delivering linear power delivery across the entire rev range. The chassis remains structurally flawless, retaining its original double-wishbone suspension geometry and near-perfect 50/50 weight distribution. Mechanically, the apex seals show optimal compression, and the five-speed manual transmission engages with bolt-action precision. Equipped with the factory Torsen limited-slip differential and four-piston braking system, this FD offers an unadulterated analog driving experience. No modifications, no leaks, just pure rotary performance in its most pristine form.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_21_listing_3",
